subject: Hello, I am George Michael, I
body:
Hello, I am George Michael, I resent this email in pending of your funds and in connection with The United Nations and IMF, as instructed to us to contact you via your email and to make sure that your ATM VISA CARD worth $10,700,000 /the document for the fund will be delivered to you through DHL.
We wish to inform you that your ATM card will expire in a few days' time if you do not use your pin before Next month, contact us with your mailing address and telephone number immediately for your ATM CARD/and document delivery.
This is urgent so I need your urgent reply to complete the delivery to you immediately.
Forward your reply to this email: 
georgemichaeltopay@petalmail.com
Regards,
George Michael

subject: Re: Hello, I am George Michael, I
body:
Hello George Michael,

Thank you for reaching out to me regarding my funds. I appreciate the information you have provided about the United Nations and IMF's involvement. It's interesting to hear that my ATM VISA CARD will be delivered to me through DHL.

Could you please provide more details about the expiration of my ATM card? I want to make sure I understand the situation correctly. Also, what is the purpose of the document delivery?

I look forward to your prompt response.

Best wishes,
Wendy
